means we have to establish Shri Ganesha. That is important.

838
00:56:24,280 --> 00:56:30,400
And then, after that we have to say the names of Vishnu,

839
00:56:30,600 --> 00:56:34,439
whatever – because His names are to be said

840
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:37,840
which are the ascending names.

841
00:56:38,175 --> 00:56:40,386
And after that

842
